<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>TierMe | Rank Your Life</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="logo.png" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0e0e10 0%, #1a1c2b 100%);
      color: white;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    header, section, footer {
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .cta {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    input[type="email"] {
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
      width: 60%;
    }
    button {
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background-color: #7c3aed;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    footer {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <img src="logo.png" alt="TierMe Logo" class="logo" />
    <h1>Your Life, Ranked by Rarity</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Compare. Compete. Improve.</p>
    <p>Discover your strengths and find out where you stand. Track your progress. Grow your tier.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <form name="waitlist" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="waitlist" />
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required />
        <button type="submit">Join the Waitlist</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </header>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 TierMe. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
